    "description": "透過課堂之講解及研究主題之進行及發表，探討設計思潮發展背後之社會、文化、經濟、族群及產業之間的互動關係，並進而探討設計之角色及未來發展之可能性。<br>Through the lectures and the research and development of the subject, we explore the interaction between society, culture, economy, ethnicity and industry behind the development of design thinking, and then explore the role of design and the possibility of future development",
